# Viterex paths and settings live in the Redaxo backend (AddOns → ViteRex → Settings),
# persisted to `rex_config` and synced to `var/data/addons/viterex/structure.json`.
# Most projects need nothing here — `.env` is only for env-driven overrides of the few
# values the Vite plugin doesn't read from `structure.json`.

# Optional: override Vite dev server URL/port detected from the hot file.
# VITE_DEV_SERVER=http://localhost
# VITE_DEV_SERVER_PORT=5173
